{"tid":1078711,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"開估！Apple上架iPhone SE特別版　","createTime":"2019-03-26T12:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T23:21:34.000Z","uid":7179,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9ca2cb4aaa6f1873a545d571bb955ed401e6181e","tid":1078711,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:34:33.000Z","msg":"美國蘋果公司（Apple Inc.）今天凌晨舉行春季發表會，雖然未發布硬體產品，不過，Apple還是在美國官網悄悄上架iPhone SE特別版，包括32GB及128GB版本，共有4個配色可以選擇，分別是銀色、灰色、玫瑰金和金色，其中32GB價格249美元（約7695元台幣）、128GB價格為299美元（約9240元台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n根據騰訊網報導，這兩個版本相比之前的原價分別便宜100和150美元，不過，目前iPhone SE特別版僅限於美國，並未在其他國家推出。<br />\n <br />\niPhone SE發布於2016年，搭載4吋Retina顯示幕、A9處理器、Touch ID、1200萬畫素主鏡頭，儘管消費者期待Apple在春季發表會發布iPhone SE 2，但希望卻落空。（財經中心／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190326/1540000/?fbclid=IwAR3xnUAAu6PVMBBbNdiUQKRmvbV0Hz6KKU8UTqJN9NndA3T2xXmZhk_Z7qE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190326%2F1540000%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3xnUAAu6PVMBBbNdiUQKRmvbV0Hz6KKU8UTqJN9NndA3T2xXmZhk_Z7qE&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=9c5d7da4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190326%2F1540000%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3xnUAAu6PVMBBbNdiUQKRmvbV0Hz6KKU8UTqJN9NndA3T2xXmZhk_Z7qE&h=94024608\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190326/1540000/?fbclid=IwAR3xnUAAu6PVMBBbNdiUQKRmvbV0Hz6KKU8UTqJN9NndA3T2xXmZhk_Z7qE</a>"},{"pid":"050b0f103d55682bd17cd90e34ae3b181e09442d","tid":1078711,"uid":213877,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"噴下色又話特別版<br />\n不過都成村人衝去買嫁啦"},{"pid":"cfa0c56f87976a5a72544a812c17620a28127fe8","tid":1078711,"uid":236429,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"翻新機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742f693c54243bad91ae54d4f35db7a627ec7e2c","tid":